<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>286</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chawlhdamna gam ngaiin ka mau,
 Bangtik leh ka tung dem?
 Bangtik leh ka galthuom kawih in,
 Muong takin ka um dem?

[V2]
 Lal na chuh sem hitiu,
 Isu hung kit macheng;
 Lalna chuh sem hitiu,
 A In a umkhawm ding.

[V3]
 2. Lei chungah kipahna umlo,
 Lungmuonna la umlo;
 Khawvel hi ka In ahi puoi,
 Dahna gamgaw ahi.

[V4]
 3. Chawldam di'n Krista kawm ka zuon,
 Vakmang talo ding leh;
 A ang sung bel dingin ei hilh,
 Van Ina ei puih man.

[V5]
 4. Hukdampa kawm chuh ka zuon tai,
 Vakmang talo ding in;
 Thihna lui ei kaihpih intin,
 Ka van In chuh tung ka.</lyrics>
<title>WE'LL WORK TILL JESUS COME</title>
</song>